{"tid":1558633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"危急！膊頭有花嘅全部同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-10T13:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T14:15:04.000Z","uid":240555,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed208d8eb0e503b67e2813f206df26ecfc216b5","tid":1558633,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"我地其實已經有好多核彈，都爆埋。<br />\n721，831，新狗嶺骨折事件，裸體搜身事件。<br />\n再包括眾多亂用臥底，催淚彈，亂棍打人。<br />\n全部都好多人知，好多人信，好多人嬲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但政府無傷，HP 仲高左！</span></span><br />\n佢地已經完全捨棄民望，國際聲譽，甚至經濟。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢地冇弱點！</span><br />\n唔好再同我講乜野春袋果啲，<br />\n甚至出現過嘅核彈已經全部全疫，因為擋到一次佢已經唔駛再理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警仲要係咁上神裝，成個港共加黨鐵無限供裝課金畀佢地...<br />\n我地而家唔係面對緊三萬個警察，<br />\n係全世界最大嘅犯罪集團。<br />\n<br />\n甚至記者都已經驅趕，鏡頭唔能夠常在，每一個位都變成暗角。<br />\n<br />\n經過埋今日警察記者會，最尾一段有提及因應場運動暴力情況。佢近乎明示喺任何行動裡面都<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以假設對方有利器或致命武器</span></span>去作出拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n加埋休班警宜家可以隨便拎棍打人，去執法。<br />\n而家黑警任何武力已經係被當作：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完全合理</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無上限武力</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以非人道</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以隨時執法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線本身仲可以加埋 傳媒鏡頭，人道條件去保護。<br />\n但而家好似就黎消失。。<br />\n<br />\n前線已經要承受無比風險，仲要無限零輸出。<br />\n唔好再屌前線去逃走，走多一個好過冇。。<br />\n<br />\n由而家開始。<br />\n<br />\n要重申<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 不受傷，不被捕，齊上齊落</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女義士一個都唔可以被捕! </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">寧願錯失一百次機會, 都唔可以失誤一次畀人捉!因為畀人捉到真係可以消失。。 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n場運動我地已經冇可能再單打獨鬥，要趕緊求外國援助。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再無限放大《香港民主人權法》，佢係必要，但得呢個我地遠遠未夠！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n本人太廢，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拜託大家用盡力去諗點行落去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地已經冇再輸嘅空間。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf3e435da60f4128cddac14b937652a6dab49ed","tid":1558633,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:59:00.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"7badabf9987ea5f1d9a0b6b56037acd763e3caad","tid":1558633,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"0b8ce8530965e908f5163716acab88167fad7493","tid":1558633,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52dfc10410275ac73fbc5d260046a166ee0ca59c","tid":1558633,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:00:37.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"25b6eb238b7500dbb7a368d3407ca65a41a4cbbd","tid":1558633,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b8ce8530965e908f5163716acab88167fad7493","tid":1558633,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:02:12.000Z","msg":"認同。。但真係未能夠用到，<br />\n好怕好快警察可以亂開真槍。。"},{"pid":"abf09889c4b3ae1c4cdebcd024e8b4d6b40bdea3","tid":1558633,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"另外，求用百萬計嘅和理非加入不合作運動。<br />\n工會教協同我出哂黎！"},{"pid":"1beda2fab99a1ddd81bfc6a06e5e9da293800269","tid":1558633,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"下一步咪升級到全球反中，目標係929全球集會反中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82123a4ce0569b5c86ca19c4b75e89845fcc4392","tid":1558633,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:10:25.000Z","msg":"充份體現左無恥便無敵呢個道理<br />\n真係冇弱點<br />\n唔知可以點做"},{"pid":"f4cf300d83f643260d9c7e641cf2c2e0af7f25ce","tid":1558633,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1beda2fab99a1ddd81bfc6a06e5e9da293800269","tid":1558633,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"下一步咪升級到全球反中，目標係929全球集會反中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲支爆啦，香港撐得好辛苦"},{"pid":"a254e5714c448bb526ba9e5ad105942f97c34ae9","tid":1558633,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:12:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">男義士都唔可以畀人捉<br />\n所以有手足不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e145f505cb821847902d2c514d6281e12c53a69c","tid":1558633,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4cf300d83f643260d9c7e641cf2c2e0af7f25ce","tid":1558633,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1beda2fab99a1ddd81bfc6a06e5e9da293800269","tid":1558633,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"下一步咪升級到全球反中，目標係929全球集會反中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲支爆啦，香港撐得好辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:15:04.000Z","msg":"上兵伐谋 其次伐交 其次伐兵 其下攻城<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}